Description:
A home on around 560sqsm with great potential
Well built and impressively maintained throughout its life, this home on a flat block of around 560sqm provides many options for its new owner including the option to renovate and add value or start from scratch and build a luxurious new family home (STCA). With light paint tones and updated carpets throughout, the home features a generous lounge, a separate family room and large modern kitchen with an included meals area. There are 3 bedrooms that all feature built in wardrobes as well as a family bathroom, a separate toilet, full laundry, a study/utility room and ducted heating. Outside, there's a double carport, a single garage and workshop plus a north facing backyard that is easy to maintain. And from here you can easily access buses, walking tracks and Eastlink with Dandenong train station, Dandenong South Primary School and all of central Dandenong's facilities just minutes away.

Description:
Expect to be impressed
If you're ready to take the plunge, you can't go past this fantastic entry level residence. Perfect for first-time buyers, investors or those looking to downsize, this two-bedroom home represents a genuinely savvy investment.
Currently tenanted and recently renovated, it features a new kitchen, stylish bathroom with separate bath/shower and glossy porcelain tiles and new carpets throughout. But it's the unit's outstanding location that really sets it apart from many others.
Situated in the prized older section of Dandenong, it's just a short walk from the shops, cafés, cinemas and Dandenong Plaza as well as the thriving Lonsdale Street Hub. Buses, trains, medical centres and the excellent Dandenong Market, it's all here in this up-and-coming satellite city. Active residents will enjoy the home's proximity to sporting clubs and the walking tracks and outdoor gym equipment of Pultney Street Park, just two blocks down the hill.
And there's no shortage of schools nearby, including St Mary's Catholic Primary School on the next corner. Extras include a lock up garage plus an extra car spot on title, gas heating, air conditioning, day/night blinds and external awnings, BIRs and super secure entry. It's one of only three units in a well-maintained complex, offering a convenient lifestyle at an affordable price.
-Secure & serene 2-bedroom home close to shops, transport & parkland
-Spacious rooms including formal lounge & light filled kitchen/meals area
-Private north-facing paved courtyard with pergola
-Lock-up garage, plus extra car space on title
Don't miss this unique opportunity.

Description:
Fully Renovated, All That’s Missing Is You!
What a beautiful place to call home or an ideal investment. Subject to a full inside/outside renovation, this home positively sparkles.
Featuring 3 good sized bedrooms, spacious open plan lounge/dining and kitchen area, everything is new here, from the roof, guttering & windows, to the fabulous kitchen with 40mm stone tops & s/steel appliances.
This home also features a freshly painted bathroom, quality blinds, LED lights, polished hardwood flooring, ducted heating and split system A/C.
All of this set behind a secure front fence, with long driveway and double garage giving plenty of off street parking, concreted entertaining area and grassed backyard complete with garden shed is sure to please. Popular location close to Dandenong Train station and CBD, easy access to Dandenong Bypass, Eastlink and other major arterials, bring the family and make this gem yours today!
